# 🚀 AI EDA Tool – Application Module

## Overview

The **AI EDA Tool App** is the core application layer of the project, designed to automate and simplify RTL design analysis, verification, debugging, visualization, and hardware estimation workflows using Artificial Intelligence.

This application integrates:

* Verilog RTL parsing
* AI-powered RTL analysis
* Error detection & correction
* Testbench generation
* Truth table generation
* Schematic visualization
* PPA (Power, Performance, Area) estimation
* Logic classification
* Interactive web-based UI

The goal of this project is to build an intelligent next-generation Electronic Design Automation (EDA) platform for semiconductor and FPGA design workflows.

---

# 📂 Folder Purpose

This folder contains:

* Backend application logic
* Flask web server
* RTL analysis pipeline
* AI integration modules
* Schematic generation utilities
* UI templates and routing
* Verification and synthesis support scripts

---

# ⚡ Features

## ✅ RTL Upload & Analysis

* Upload Verilog RTL files
* Parse module information automatically
* Detect syntax and structural issues
* Generate module summaries

## ✅ AI-Powered RTL Debugging

* AI-assisted code correction
* RTL optimization suggestions
* Cleaner and synthesizable code generation

## ✅ Testbench Generator

* Automatic Verilog testbench generation
* Input stimulus generation
* Simulation-ready outputs

## ✅ Truth Table Generator

* Generates combinational logic truth tables
* Useful for verification and debugging

## ✅ Schematic Generator

* Converts RTL into gate-level schematic visualization
* Printable schematic support
* SVG schematic rendering

## ✅ PPA Estimation

* Area estimation
* Timing estimation
* Power approximation
* Technology-aware synthesis flow

## ✅ Logic Classification

Automatically identifies:

* Combinational Circuits
* Sequential Circuits
* FSM-based Designs
* Arithmetic Modules
* Memory-related Logic

