# ▶️ Running the Application

## 1️⃣ Activate OSS CAD Suite

```bash
environment.bat
```

## 2️⃣ Run Flask Application

```bash
python app.py
```

## 3️⃣ Open Browser

```bash
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

